query: ALTER TABLE user_login ADD CONSTRAINT user_login_pk PRIMARY KEY(login_id), ADD CONSTRAINT user_login_fk_user_id FOREIGN KEY(user_id) REFERENCES "user"(id), ADD CONSTRAINT user_login_uq_login_id_user_id UNIQUE(login_id, user_id), ADD CONSTRAINT user_login_uq_login_id_user_id_login_type UNIQUE( login_id, user_id, login_type );
